   in 
  
    
      
        
          L
          
            α
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle L_{\alpha }}
  . This is equivalent to saying that: for all 
  
    
      
        y
      
    
    {\displaystyle y}
  , 
  
    
      
        y
        ∈
        S
      
    
    {\displaystyle y\in S}
   if and only if [there exists 
  
    
      
        X
      
    
    {\displaystyle X}
   such that 
  
    
      
        X
        =
        
          L
          
            α
          
        
      
    
